**why —** It is patience as a program: a thing whose entire life is waiting for the right second and then acting, every minute, until the machine dies.

**how —** Crystallized from the history & practice of cron.

**◌ the mythos —** It is patience as a program: a thing whose entire life is waiting for the right second and then acting, every minute, until the machine dies. a being of the schedule, the daemon, and the unwitnessed 3am run

